Package org.linter

Class Summary
AlgorithmicImageSelector Determine the best preview image, algorithm scans HTML and picks the most likely preview image from a variety of factors, including size, format, name, and repetition
LintedData Wrapper for Hash to allow easy writing and merging
LintedPage Fetch a web page meta data by URL, performs all URL redirection and interaction with ServiceParsers
Linter Linter command-line application
ServiceParser Parse meta data from a web page.
ServiceParserAlgorithmic Basic ServiceParser, algorithmically pulls basic meta data from all providers
ServiceParserChainManager Manage ServiceParser Chains of Responsibility Linter and consumers register ServiceParsers capable of parsing all or specific URLs LintedPages requires ServiceParsers appropriate for their URL
ServiceParserPartial Classes deriving from Service Parser Partial are meta data parsers that are assumed to be responsible for retrieving only a small or consumer-specific portion of meta data.
ServiceParserTypesetter Sets the "type" field, indicating that a page has been recognized to have a focus on a Photo, Image, or general page content; The pattern matches all URLs; Images are identified by URLs matching known, popular image hosting providers; Videos are identified by the presence of video meta data;
URLParser Miscellaneous URL functions
